<br>
I've had great religious discussions, lots of fun bartering, and some pretty wacky experiences (Hey, I'm a Bristlebane bard, what can I say?) I've also been in groups where its Kill Kill Kill...there's enough of both though that you can find what you are looking fairly easily I think...as an evil race it will be a bit harder to travel (especially without the boats) this will make it harder to find people to fit your style I think.<br>
<br>
I didn't find a whole lot of RP until about level 10ish, then it seemed that a few doors opened up...but I also have travelled all over the place meeting people, give it some time.<br>
<br>
I wouldn't worry about the twinks...more loot for you anyway, skill is hard, equipment is easy...and twinks can RP as well as the next guy if they want to.<br>
